webpackJsonp([0xbf22902c300e],{495:function(e,t){e.exports={data:{markdownRemark:{html:'<p>Hello World in 3D for Blender with a render out in VR acceptable.</p>\n<ol>\n<li><a href="http://blender-vr-manual.readthedocs.io/installation/installation-manual.html">Download blender and BlendVR</a></li>\n<li>\n<p>Open your first document and learn the basics of the interface:</p>\n<iframe width="560" height="315"\nsrc="https://www.youtube.com/embed/kes2qmijy7w" frameborder="0"\ngesture="media" allow="encrypted-media" allowfullscreen></iframe>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>Create the text</p>\n<div style="position:relative;height:0;padding-bottom:56.25%"><iframe\nsrc="https://www.youtube.com/embed/74pUyg2LWro?ecver=2" width="640"\nheight="360" frameborder="0" gesture="media" allow="encrypted-media"\nstyle="position:absolute;width:100%;height:100%;left:0"\nallowfullscreen></iframe></div>\n</li>\n<li>Add in the world.\nYou can\n<a href="https://www.blendswap.com/blends/search?keywords=earth&#x26;is_fan_art=1&#x26;blend_license=&#x26;render_engine=&#x26;sort=edit_date&#x26;direction=desc">search</a>\nfor earth models at <a href="https://www.blendswap.com/">blendswap</a>\nI am going to use <a href="https://www.blendswap.com/blends/view/22444">this</a>\none. We\'ll start by importing the model and then replacing the dot\nunder our exclamation point with our earth model.</li>\n<li>Add in the camera orbit.\n<a href="https://blender.stackexchange.com/questions/3476/how-can-i-animate-the-camera-in-a-perfect-circular-rotation-around-a-fixed-posit">Example stack exchange question about circlular motion</a></li>\n<li>Render.\n<a href="https://blender.stackexchange.com/questions/39190/rendering-3d-video-image-for-google-cardboard">Example stack exchange question about blender rendering for G cardboard</a></li>\n</ol>\n<p>And your first hello world in 3D has been done. Enjoy!</p>\n<p>Now go and try some more blender <a href="https://www.blender.org/support/tutorials/">tutorials</a>.</p>\n<p>And, also, <a href="https://cloud.blender.org/welcome">cloud.blender.com</a> is\nanother official place from the blender team where they have a great collection\nof tutorials.</p>\n<p>There is also a <a href="https://www.blendswap.com/">great place for getting models</a>.</p>',frontmatter:{title:"H3ll0 Blender"}}},pathContext:{slug:"/hello3dworld-blender/"}}}});
